 posterior inference and evaluate frequentist properties via\nsimulations. We use our model to assess the cost-efficacy of chemotherapy\nversus radiation adjuvant therapy for treating endometrial cancer in the\nSEER-Medicare database.\n","versions":[{"version":"v1","created":"Tue, 11 Feb 2020 21:51:58 GMT"},{"version":"v2","created":"Tue, 8 Sep 2020 22:28:22 GMT"}],"update_date":"2020-09-10"}
